{
  "chapter": "114",
  "title": "东越列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "闽越东瓯立国",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">闽越</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无诸</span>和<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东海</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：东海王摇\">摇（东海王摇）</span>，他们的祖先都是<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>的后代，姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">驺氏</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝吞并天下之后，两人都被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">废</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">君长</span>，把他们的地方设置为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">闽中郡</span>。等到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">畔</span>离<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝的时候，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无诸</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：东海王摇\">摇（东海王摇）</span>率领<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>人归附了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">鄱阳令</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴芮</span>，也就是所谓的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">鄱君</span>，跟随<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝。当时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>主持分封，没有立他们为王，因此他们不<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">附</span>从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>的时候，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无诸</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：东海王摇\">摇（东海王摇）</span>率领<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>人辅佐<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>，又重新<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无诸</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">闽越</span>王，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">王</span>领<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">闽中</span>故地，定都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东冶</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">孝惠三年</span>，推举<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>时期<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>人的功劳，说<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">闽君</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：东海王摇\">摇（东海王摇）</span>功劳多，他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众也乐于归附，于是<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：东海王摇\">摇（东海王摇）</span>为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东海</span>王，定都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东瓯</span>，世人俗称为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">东瓯王</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "东瓯从吴与杀吴王",
      "text": "过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数世（时长）</span>，到<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">孝景三年</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘濞\">濞（刘濞）</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>叛，想要联合<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">闽越</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">闽越</span>不肯出兵，只有<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">东瓯</span>追随<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>。等到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>灭，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">东瓯</span>接受了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝的悬赏，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">丹徒</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span>，因此都得以免于<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀，返回封国。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "闽越围东瓯",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子驹</span>逃亡到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">闽越</span>，怨恨<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">东瓯</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲，常常劝说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">闽越</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">东瓯</span>。到<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">建元三年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">闽越</span>发兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">东瓯</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">东瓯</span>粮食耗尽，处境危困，即将投降，就派人向<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>告急。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>询问<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田蚡</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田蚡\">蚡（田蚡）</span>回答说：\"<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>人互相<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>，本来是常有的事，又屡次<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>覆不定，不值得烦劳<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>前去救援。从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝时就已经<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">弃</span>之不管了。\" 于是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄助</span>反驳<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田蚡\">蚡（田蚡）</span>说：\"只怕是力量不够救援，恩德不够覆庇；如果真能做到，为何要<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">弃</span>之不管？况且<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝连<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>都<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">弃</span>了，何况是<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>地！如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">小国</span>因困窘前来向<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>告急，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>不去救援，他们还能到哪里去申诉呢？又凭什么去<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>养<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万国</span>呢？\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>不值得与他商议。我刚即位，不想拿出<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">虎符</span>发动郡国的兵。\" 于是派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄助</span>持<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">节</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>调发军队。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太守</span>想抗拒不肯发兵，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄助\">助（庄助）</span>就<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>了一名<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司马</span>，表明皇上的旨意，于是调发军队浮海救援<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">东瓯</span>。军队还没到，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">闽越</span>就已引兵撤离。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">东瓯</span>请求举国<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">徙</span>入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>，于是全部民众迁来，安置在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江淮</span>之间。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "闽越击南越与郢被杀",
      "text": "到<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">建元六年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">闽越</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>恪守<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>的约定，不敢擅自发兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>退而是上报朝廷。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>派遣<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大行</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王恢</span>从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">豫章</span>出兵，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大农</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩安国</span>从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>出兵，都任命为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>。军队尚未翻越山岭，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">闽越</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：闽越王郢\">郢（闽越王郢）</span>就发兵据守险要。他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">馀善</span>就与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宗族</span>商议说：\"王擅自发兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>，没有请示朝廷，所以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>派兵来<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>讨。现在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军兵多势强，即使侥幸取胜，后续军队会更多，最终会<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>国才停。现在如果<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了王向<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>谢罪。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>如果听从，罢兵，国家就能保全；如果不听，就拼力<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>斗；不胜，就逃亡入海。\" 大家都说\"好\"。于是用矛<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>死了王，派使者捧着王的头送到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大行</span>那里。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大行</span>说：\"之所以派兵来，是为了<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>讨王。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今王</span>的头已经送到，谢了罪，不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>而罢兵，没有比这更有利的了。\" 于是就便宜行事按兵不动，告知<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大农</span>的军队，并派使者带着王的头快马报告<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>。皇帝下诏让两位将军<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">罢</span>兵，说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：闽越王郢\">郢（闽越王郢）</span>等人是首恶，只有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无诸</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>子<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">繇君</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：繇君丑\">丑（繇君丑）</span>没有参与谋划。\" 于是派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎中将</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：繇君丑\">丑（繇君丑）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越繇王</span>，奉守<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">闽越</span>祖先的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">祭祀</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">馀善</span>已经<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：闽越王郢\">郢（闽越王郢）</span>，在国中威行显赫，国<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>大多归附于他，他私自<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span>为王。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">繇王</span>不能矫正约束他的众人、坚守正道。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>听说后，认为不值得为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">馀善</span>再次兴师，说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">馀善</span>屡次与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：闽越王郢\">郢（闽越王郢）</span>谋划作乱，而后又带头<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：闽越王郢\">郢（闽越王郢）</span>，军队得以不必劳顿。\" 于是<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">馀善</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">东越王</span>，与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">繇王</span>并立。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "余善反汉称帝",
      "text": "到<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元鼎五年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">东越王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">馀善</span>上书，请求率卒<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八千人</span>跟随<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船将军</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕嘉</span>等人。军队到了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">揭扬</span>，借口海上风浪，不前进，持两端之计，暗中派使者通<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>。等到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">番禺</span>的时候，他还是没到。当时<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">杨仆</span>派使者上书，愿意就便引兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">东越</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士卒</span>劳顿疲倦为由，不答应，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">罢</span>兵，命令各<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">校</span>驻守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">豫章</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">梅领</span>待命。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元鼎六年秋</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">馀善</span>听说<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>将军请求<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>讨他，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军即将临境，即将到来，就<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>叛了，发兵抵挡<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军道路。号称<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">驺力</span>等人为\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吞汉将军</span>\"，攻入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">白沙</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武林</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">梅岭</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军三名<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">校尉</span>。当时<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大农</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张成</span>、原先的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">山州侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：山州侯齿\">齿（山州侯齿）</span>率军驻守，不敢<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>敌，退到便利之处，都因畏敌怯懦之罪被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "汉军讨灭东越",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">馀善</span>刻了\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>\"<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">玺</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为帝，欺骗他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众，散布妄言。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">横海将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩说</span>从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">句章</span>出发，浮海从东方前往；<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">杨仆</span>从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武林</span>出发；<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王温舒</span>从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">梅岭</span>出发；<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越侯</span>担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">戈船</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">下濑将军</span>，从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">若邪</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">白沙</span>出发。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元封元年冬</span>，都进入了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">东越</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">东越</span>一向已发兵据守险要，派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">徇北将军</span>守卫<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武林</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>军的数名<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">校尉</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">长吏</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船将军</span>率领<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">钱唐</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辕终古</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">徇北将军</span>，封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御兒侯</span>。这是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>军自身未往救援的情况。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "原<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越衍侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴阳</span>先前在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>派他回去劝谕<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">馀善</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">馀善</span>不听。等到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">横海将军</span>先到，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越衍侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴阳</span>率他封邑的<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七百人</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>叛，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉阳</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>击<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>军。跟随<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">建成侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：建成侯敖\">敖（建成侯敖）</span>，与他的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">率</span>、追随<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">繇王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">居股</span>谋划说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">馀善</span>是首恶，劫持控制我们。如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军已到，军<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">众</span>强大，我们打算<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>死<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">馀善</span>，自己归顺<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军众将，或许能侥幸得以免罪。\" 于是一起<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">馀善</span>，率他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">众</span>向<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">横海将军</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">降</span>。因此<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">封</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">繇王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">居股</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">东成侯</span>，食邑<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万户</span>；<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">封</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">建成侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：建成侯敖\">敖（建成侯敖）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">开陵侯</span>；<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">封</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越衍侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴阳</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">北石侯</span>；<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">封</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">横海将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩说\">说（韩说）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">案道侯</span>；<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">封</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">横海校尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：横海校尉福\">福（横海校尉福）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">缭嫈侯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：横海校尉福\">福（横海校尉福）</span>是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成阳</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：成阳共王\">共王（成阳共王）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>，曾做过<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">海常侯</span>，因<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">坐法</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">失</span>去侯位。过去从军无功，因<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宗室</span>之故封侯。众将都没立功，没有被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">封</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">东越</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span>领<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">多军</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军一到，就<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">弃</span>军<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">降</span>汉，被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">封</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">无锡侯</span>。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">东越</span>地势狭窄多险阻，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">闽越</span>彪悍，屡次<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>覆，下诏命<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">军吏</span>都率领当地的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">徙</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江淮</span>之间安置。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">东越</span>之地于是空虚。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "太史公论赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>虽然是<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蛮夷</span>，他们的祖先难道曾经对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众有大功大德吗，何以延续如此之久！经历数代常常做<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君王</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>还曾一度称霸。 然而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">馀善</span>大逆不道，国家被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>、民<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">众</span>被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">迁</span>，其先人<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">苗裔</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">繇王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">居股</span>等人尚且被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">封</span>为<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万户</span>侯，由此可知<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>人世世代代都做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">公</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>。 大概是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>的遗泽吧。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>的后裔，称为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无诸</span>。 既借<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝之宠，实是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝之余。 <span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">驺</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">骆</span>为姓氏，居住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">闽中</span>。 王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：东海王摇\">摇（东海王摇）</span>被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东隅</span>安<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">处</span>。 后嗣无道，自相<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>锄。"
    }
  }
